sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ODHWebhook as ODH Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ODHCtrl as odh-notebook-controller
    participant KFCtrl as notebook-controller
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Notebook as Notebook Pod<br/>8888/TCP HTTP

    Note over User, Notebook: Flow 1: Notebook Creation and Access (Auth-Enabled)

    User->>K8sAPI: 1. Create Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>ODHWebhook: 2. Mutating webhook call<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS (service CA)
    Note right of ODHWebhook: Inject kube-rbac-proxy sidecar<br/>Inject DSPA/MLflow/Feast config<br/>Resolve ImageStream images
    ODHWebhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Notebook
    K8sAPI->>ODHWebhook: Validating webhook call<br/>HTTPS/8443
    ODHWebhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated

    par ODH Controller Reconciliation
        ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: 6. Create HTTPRoute, ReferenceGrant,<br/>NetworkPolicy, kube-rbac-proxy resources<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    and Notebook Controller Reconciliation
        KFCtrl->>K8sAPI: 4-5. Create StatefulSet + Service<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    end

    Note over User, Notebook: User Accesses Notebook

    User->>Gateway: 7. GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBP: 8. Forward to kube-rbac-proxy<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: 9. TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Auth OK (user has 'get' on notebooks)
    KRBP->>Notebook: 10. Proxy to notebook<br/>HTTP/8888, localhost
    Notebook-->>KRBP: Jupyter response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: Notebook UI

    Note over User, Notebook: Flow 2: Notebook Idle Culling

    loop Every IDLENESS_CHECK_PERIOD (default: 1 min)
        KFCtrl->>Notebook: 1-3. Poll /api/kernels, /api/terminals<br/>HTTP/8888, No Auth
        Notebook-->>KFCtrl: Kernel/terminal status
    end
    Note right of KFCtrl: If idle > CULL_IDLE_TIME (default: 1440 min)
    KFCtrl->>K8sAPI: 4. Patch Notebook annotation<br/>(kubeflow-resource-stopped)
    KFCtrl->>K8sAPI: 5. Scale StatefulSet to 0 replicas

    Note over User, Notebook: Flow 3: DSPA Pipeline Secret Injection

    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: 1. Read DSPA CR ('dspa' in namespace)<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: 2. Read S3 credential Secret<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: 3. Create/update ds-pipeline-config Secret<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
